# Story Structure Template

## Typical narrative arc

### Act 1 - Setup (chapters 1-X)
- Establish normal world
- Introduce characters
- Inciting incident

### Act 2A - Rising action (chapters X-Y)
- Characters investigate/explore
- Discover clues
- Face minor obstacles

### Act 2B - Complications (chapters Y-Z)
- Major setback
- Stakes increase
- False leads

### Act 3 - Climax & Resolution (chapters Z-end)
- Confrontation
- Resolution of mystery
- Return to normal

